{"data":[{"name":"70:1","price":"സംഭവിക്കാനിരിക്കുന്ന ഒരു ശിക്ഷയെ ഒരു ചോദ്യകര്‍ത്താവ് അതാ ആവശ്യപ്പെട്ടിരിക്കുന്നു.(1)","arabic":"سَأَلَ سَآئِلُۢ بِعَذَابٖ وَاقِعٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5376,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"1) 'സഅല' എന്ന പദത്തിന് ചോദിച്ചുവെന്നും ആവശ്യപ്പെട്ടുവെന്നും അര്‍ഥമുണ്ട്.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"sa-ala sāilun biʿadhābin wāqiʿin ","translations":["Asked","a questioner","about a punishment","bound to happen","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["sa-ala","sāilun","biʿadhābin","wāqiʿin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,720],[2,720,3789],[3,3789,6089],[4,6089,7264]]}},{"name":"70:2","price":"സത്യനിഷേധികള്‍ക്ക് അത് തടുക്കുവാന്‍ ആരുമില്ല.","arabic":"لِّلۡكَٰفِرِينَ لَيۡسَ لَهُۥ دَافِعٞ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5377,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"lil'kāfirīna laysa lahu dāfiʿun ","translations":["To the disbelievers","not","of it","any preventer","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["lil'kāfirīna","laysa","lahu","dāfiʿun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1730],[2,1730,2520],[3,2520,3080],[4,3080,4395]]}},{"name":"70:3","price":"കയറിപ്പോകുന്ന വഴികളുടെ അധിപനായ അല്ലാഹുവിങ്കല്‍ നിന്ന് വരുന്ന (ശിക്ഷയെ).","arabic":"مِّنَ ٱللَّهِ ذِي ٱلۡمَعَارِجِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5378,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"mina al-lahi dhī al-maʿāriji ","translations":["From","Allah","Owner","(of) the ways of ascent","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["mina","al-lahi","dhī","al-maʿāriji",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,1430],[3,1430,1620],[4,1620,2935]]}},{"name":"70:4","price":"അമ്പതിനായിരം കൊല്ലത്തിന്‍റെ അളവുള്ളതായ ഒരു ദിവസത്തില്‍ മലക്കുകളും ആത്മാവും അവങ്കലേക്ക് കയറിപ്പോകുന്നു.","arabic":"تَعۡرُجُ ٱلۡمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ وَٱلرُّوحُ إِلَيۡهِ فِي يَوۡمٖ كَانَ مِقۡدَارُهُۥ خَمۡسِينَ أَلۡفَ سَنَةٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5379,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"taʿruju al-malāikatu wal-rūḥu ilayhi fī yawmin kāna miq'dāruhu khamsīna alfa sanatin ","translations":["Ascend","the Angels","and the Spirit","to Him","in","a Day","[is]","its measure","(is) fifty","thousand","year(s)","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["taʿruju","al-malāikatu","wal-rūḥu","ilayhi","fī","yawmin","kāna","miq'dāruhu","khamsīna","alfa","sanatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,870],[2,870,3970],[3,3970,4970],[4,4970,5780],[5,5780,6210],[6,6210,7900],[7,7900,8480],[8,8480,9920],[9,9920,10990],[10,10990,11580],[11,11580,12765]]}},{"name":"70:5","price":"എന്നാല്‍ (നബിയേ,) നീ ഭംഗിയായ ക്ഷമ കൈക്കൊള്ളുക.","arabic":"فَٱصۡبِرۡ صَبۡرٗا جَمِيلًا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5380,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-iṣ'bir ṣabran jamīlan ","translations":["So be patient","a patience","good","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-iṣ'bir","ṣabran","jamīlan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,780],[2,780,2270],[3,2270,3965]]}},{"name":"70:6","price":"തീര്‍ച്ചയായും അവര്‍ അതിനെ വിദൂരമായി കാണുന്നു.","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ يَرَوۡنَهُۥ بَعِيدٗا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5381,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"innahum yarawnahu baʿīdan ","translations":["Indeed, they","see it","(as) far off","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["innahum","yarawnahu","baʿīdan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1680],[2,1680,2910],[3,2910,4165]]}},{"name":"70:7","price":"നാം അതിനെ അടുത്തതായും കാണുന്നു.","arabic":"وَنَرَىٰهُ قَرِيبٗا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5382,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wanarāhu qarīban ","translations":["But We see it","near","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wanarāhu","qarīban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,2705]]}},{"name":"70:8","price":"ആകാശം ഉരുകിയ ലോഹം പോലെ ആകുന്ന ദിവസം!","a