They will be made to see each other","Would wish","the criminal","if","he (could be) ransomed","from","(the) punishment","(of) that Day","by his children","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["yubaṣṣarūnahum","yawaddu","al-muj'rimu","law","yaftadī","min","ʿadhābi","yawmi-idhin","bibanīhi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2540],[2,2540,3300],[3,3300,4290],[4,4290,4680],[5,4680,5750],[6,5750,6080],[7,6080,6940],[8,6940,8870],[9,8870,12485]]}},{"name":"70:12","price":"തന്‍റെ ഭാര്യയെയും സഹോദരനെയും","arabic":"وَصَٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَأَخِيهِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5387,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"waṣāḥibatihi wa-akhīhi ","translations":["And his spouse","and his brother","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["waṣāḥibatihi","wa-akhīhi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1810],[2,1810,4775]]}},{"name":"70:13","price":"തനിക്ക് അഭയം നല്‍കിയിരുന്ന തന്‍റെ ബന്ധുക്കളെയും","arabic":"وَفَصِيلَتِهِ ٱلَّتِي تُـٔۡوِيهِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5388,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wafaṣīlatihi allatī tu'wīhi ","translations":["And his nearest kindred","who","sheltered him","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["wafaṣīlatihi","allatī","tu'wīhi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1570],[2,1570,2420],[3,2420,5215]]}},{"name":"70:14","price":"ഭൂമിയിലുള്ള മുഴുവന്‍ ആളുകളെയും. എന്നിട്ട് അതവനെ രക്ഷപ്പെടുത്തുകയും ചെയ്തിരുന്നെങ്കില്‍ എന്ന്‌.","arabic":"وَمَن فِي ٱلۡأَرۡضِ جَمِيعٗا ثُمَّ يُنجِيهِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5389,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"waman fī al-arḍi jamīʿan thumma yunjīhi ","translations":["And whoever","(is) on","the earth","all","then","it (could) save him","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["waman","fī","al-arḍi","jamīʿan","thumma","yunjīhi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1190],[2,1190,1440],[3,1440,2260],[4,2260,4089],[5,4089,5439],[6,5439,9824]]}},{"name":"70:15"