0],[3,2900,4920],[4,4920,8705]]}},{"name":"70:36","price":"അപ്പോള്‍ സത്യനിഷേധികള്‍ക്കെന്തു പറ്റി! അവര്‍ നിന്‍റെ നേരെ കഴുത്തു നീട്ടി വരുന്നു.","arabic":"فَمَالِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ قِبَلَكَ مُهۡطِعِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5411,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"famāli alladhīna kafarū qibalaka muh'ṭiʿīna ","translations":["So what is with","those who","disbelieve","before you","(they) hasten","(36)"],"transliterationArr":["famāli","alladhīna","kafarū","qibalaka","muh'ṭiʿīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,790],[2,790,1700],[3,1700,2520],[4,2520,3390],[5,3390,6335]]}},{"name":"70:37","price":"വലത്തോട്ടും ഇടത്തോട്ടും അവർ കൂട്ടങ്ങളായി ചിതറിപോകുന്നു.(4)","arabic":"عَنِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ وَعَنِ ٱلشِّمَالِ عِزِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5412,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"4) 'ഇടത്തുനിന്നും വലത്തുനിന്നും കൂട്ടങ്ങളായി അവര്‍ നിന്റെ നേര്‍ക്ക് കഴുത്തു നീട്ടി വരുന്നു' എന്നാണ് ചില വ്യാഖ്യാതാക്കള്‍ അര്‍ഥം നല്കിയിട്ടുള്ളത്.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿani al-yamīni waʿani al-shimāli ʿizīna ","translations":["On","the right","and on","the left","(in) separate groups","(37)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿani","al-yamīni","waʿani","al-shimāli","ʿizīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,450],[2,450,1420],[3,1420,1990],[4,1990,2950],[5,2950,5635]]}},{"name":"70:38","price":"സുഖാനുഭൂതിയുടെ സ്വര്‍ഗത്തില്‍ താന്‍ പ്രവേശിപ്പിക്കപ്പെടണമെന്ന് അവരില്‍ ഓരോ മനുഷ്യനും മോഹിക്കുന്നുണ്ടോ?","arabic":"أَيَطۡمَعُ كُلُّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ أَن يُدۡخَلَ جَنَّةَ نَعِيمٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5413,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"ayaṭmaʿu kullu im'ri-in min'hum an yud'khala jannata naʿīmin ","translations":["Does long","every","person","among them","that","he enters","a Garden","(of) Delight","(38)"],"transliterationArr":["ayaṭmaʿu","kullu","im'ri-in","min'hum","an","yud'khala","jannata","naʿīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1040],[2,1040,1600],[3,1600,2250],[4,2250,3800],[5,3800,5730],[6,5730,7380],[7,7380,10085]]}},{"name":"70:39","price":"അതു വേണ്ട. തീര്‍ച്ചയായും അവര്‍ക്കറിയാവുന്നതില്‍ നിന്നാണ് അവരെ നാം സൃഷ്ടിച്ചിട്ടുള്ളത്‌.(5)","arabic":"كَلَّآۖ إِنَّا خَلَقۡنَٰهُم مِّمَّا يَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5414,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"5) നിസ്സാരമായ ബീജത്തില്‍ നിന്നാണ് താന്‍ സൃഷ്ടിക്കപ്പെട്ടതെന്ന കാര്യം എല്ലാവര്‍ക്കും അറിയാം. ജന്മംകൊണ്ട് ആര്‍ക്കും സവിശേഷമായ ഒരു മഹത്വവുമില്ല. ആദര്‍ശനിഷ്ഠമായ ജീവിതരീതിയാണ് മഹത്വത്തിന് നിദാനമായിട്ടുള്ളത്.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā innā khalaqnāhum mimmā yaʿlamūna ","translations":["By no means","Indeed, We","[We] have created them","from what","they know","(39)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","innā","khalaqnāhum","mimmā","yaʿlamūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,970],[2,970,3170],[3,3170,4490],[4,4490,6550],[5,6550,9785]]}},{"name":"70:40","price":"എന്നാല്‍ ഉദയസ്ഥാനങ്ങളുടെയും അസ്തമയസ്ഥാനങ്ങളുടെയും രക്ഷിതാവിന്‍റെ പേരില്‍ ഞാന്‍ സത്യം ചെയ്തു പറയുന്നു: തീര്‍ച്ചയായും നാം കഴിവുള്ളനാണെന്ന്‌.","arabic":"فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِرَبِّ ٱلۡمَشَٰرِقِ وَٱلۡمَغَٰرِبِ إِنَّا لَقَٰدِرُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5415,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"falā uq'simu birabbi al-mashāriqi wal-maghāribi innā laqādirūna ","translations":["But nay","I swear","by (the) Lord","(of) the risings","and the settings","that We","(are) surely Able","(40)"],"transliterationArr":["falā","uq'simu","birabbi","al-mashāriqi","wal-maghāribi","innā","laqādirūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1860],[2,1860,2690],[3,2690,3440],[4,3440,4650],[5,4650,5970],[6,5970,7440],[7,7440,10645]]}},{"name":"70:41","price":"അവരെക്കാള്‍ നല്ലവരെ പകരം കൊണ്ടു വരാന്‍. നാം തോല്‍പിക്കപ്പെടുന്നവനല്ല താനും.","arabic":"عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّبَدِّلَ خَيۡرٗا مِّنۡهُمۡ وَمَا نَحۡنُ بِمَسۡبُوقِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5416,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿalā an nubaddila khayran min'hum wamā naḥnu bimasbūqīna ","translations":["[On]","to","[We] replace","(with) better","than them","and not","We","(are) to be outrun","(41)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿalā","an","nubaddila","khayran","min'hum","wamā","naḥnu","bimasbūqīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1960],[2,1960,2310],[3,2310,3890],[4,3890,4530],[5,4530,6210],[6,6210,6760],[7,6760,7370],[8,7370,10855]]}},{"name":"70:42","price":"ആകയാല്‍ അവര്‍ക്ക് താക്കീത് നല്‍കപ്പെടുന്ന അവരുടെ ആ ദിവസത്തെ അവര്‍ കണ്ടുമുട്ടുന്നത് വരെ അവര്‍ തോന്നിവാസത്തില്‍ മുഴുകുകയും കളിച്ചു കൊണ്ടിരിക്കുകയും ചെയ്യാന്‍ നീ അവരെ വിട്ടേക്കുക.","arabic":"فَذَرۡهُمۡ يَخُوضُواْ وَيَلۡعَبُواْ حَتَّىٰ يُلَٰقُواْ يَوۡمَهُمُ ٱلَّذِي يُوعَدُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5417,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"fadharhum yakhūḍū wayalʿabū ḥattā yulāqū yawmahumu alladhī yūʿadūna ","translations":["So leave them","(to) converse vainly","and amuse themselves","until","they meet","their Day","which","they are promised","(42)"],"transliterationArr":["fadharhum","yakhūḍū","wayalʿabū","ḥattā","yulāqū","yawmahumu","alladhī","yūʿadūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,2130],[3,2130,3210],[4,3210,4030],[5,4030,5020],[6,5020,6070],[7,6070,6950],[8,6950,10115]]}},{"name":"70:43","price":"അതായത് അവര്‍ ഒരു നാട്ടക്കുറിയുടെ നേരെ ധൃതിപ്പെട്ടു പോകുന്നത് പോലെ ഖബ്‌റുകളില്‍ നിന്ന് പുറപ്പെട്ടു പോകുന്ന ദിവസം.","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَخۡرُجُونَ مِنَ ٱلۡأَجۡدَاثِ سِرَاعٗا كَأَنَّهُمۡ إِلَىٰ نُصُبٖ يُوفِضُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5418,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma yakhrujūna mina al-ajdāthi sirāʿan ka-annahum ilā nuṣubin yūfiḍūna ","translations":["(The) Day","they will come out","from","the graves","rapidly","as if they (were)","to","a goal","hastening","(43)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","yakhrujūna","mina","al-ajdāthi","sirāʿan","ka-annahum","ilā","nuṣubin","yūfiḍūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,1770],[3,1770,2140],[4,2140,3350],[5,3350,4950],[6,4950,6910],[7,6910,7510],[8,7510,8950],[9,8950,12385]]}},{"name":"70:44","price":"അവരുടെ കണ്ണുകള്‍ കീഴ്പോട്ട് താണിരിക്കും. അപമാനം അവരെ ആവരണം ചെയ്തിരിക്കും. അതാണ് അവര്‍ക്ക് താക്കീത് നല്‍കപ്പെട്ടിരുന്ന ദിവസം.","arabic":"خَٰشِعَةً أَبۡصَٰرُهُمۡ تَرۡهَقُهُمۡ ذِلَّةٞۚ ذَٰلِكَ ٱلۡيَوۡمُ ٱلَّذِي كَانُواْ يُوعَدُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5419,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"khāshiʿatan abṣāruhum tarhaquhum dhillatun dhālika al-yawmu alladhī kānū yūʿadūna ","translations":["Humbled","their eyesights","will cover them","humiliation","That","(is) the Day","which","they were","promised","(44)"],"transliterationArr":["khāshiʿatan","abṣāruhum","tarhaquhum","dhillatun","dhālika","al-yawmu","alladhī","kānū","yūʿadūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,2620],[3,2620,3740],[4,3740,5200],[5,5200,6050],[6,6050,6780],[7,6780,7800],[8,7800,8750],[9,8750,14165]]}}],"chapter":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij","Chapter Al-Ma'arij","Ma'arij","Surah Ma'arij","Chapter Ma'arij","Al Ma'arij","Surah Al Ma'arij","Chapter Al Ma'arij","Surah 70","Chapter 70","The Ascending Stairways","المعارج"],"version":{"key":"malayalam_kunhi","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ml","version":"1.0.3","last_update":1622322000,"title":"Malayalam translation - Abdul-Hamid Haidar Al-Madany and Kanhi Muhammad","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Malayalam by Abdul-Hamid Haidar Al-Madany and Kanhi Muhammad."}}